          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Truth in Buffalo Labeling Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the sale of food that contains water buffalo and is labeled as <em>buffalo</em> unless the specific term used in the labeling is <em>water buffalo</em>.</p>]]>
